Package: prana-elex
Version: @VERSION@
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: @VENDOR@
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED_SIZE@
Depends: libc6, libstdc++6, libgcc-s1, libasound2, libportaudio2, libsndfile1, libgl1, libegl1, libxkbcommon-x11-0, libxcb-cursor0
Description: PRANA ELEX marine VHF transcription and translation
 Desktop client for PRANA ELEX SaaS. Google Cloud credentials and provider
 integrations remain on the PRANA backend.
